  { NVM

    NVM = Non-volatile memory («nichtflüchtiger Speicher»)  

    Compare with nvm = *node version manager*.

  }
  { Thunderbolt

   *Thunderbolt* is the brand name of an interface for connection of external peripherals to a computer. It combines
      • PCI Express (PCIe) and
      • Display Port (DP)

    Thunderbolt provides DC power.


    Thunderbolt was developed by Intel in collaboration with Apple.

    Thunderbolt was initially marketed under the name *Light Peak*.j

  }

